Orrefors glassworks (also known as just Orrefors) is a glassworks in the Swedish village Orrefors in Sm√•land. Orrefors manufactures high-quality crystal glassware and art glass. The range consists of crystal stemware, barware, vases, and sculptures and lighting products in crystal.
Orrefors was a part of the Swedish glassworks group Orrefors Kosta Boda AB.
